review:
The game is a great game. You might think it would be a rip off breath of the wild which is what I thought at first glance. But once I got to play the game there is a great amount of things with this game. You can wish characters, there is great music, several bosses. I recommend you try the game out first before giving any judgement on the game. I swear you might like it if your into breath of the wild and open world games along with anime art styles. 
